      "title": "Court rejects police request against protests near President\u2019s House",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Colombo Magistrate\u2019s Court has rejected a request made by the police to issue a restraining order preventing the protest marches planned for tomorrow (July 08) and the day after (July 09) near the President\u2019s House."
